@startuml Design_Methodology_Flowchart
title Fig: Design Methodology (SLM Story Generator)\n— aligned with application-based LLM project lifecycle

skinparam backgroundColor #FEFEFE
skinparam defaultFontName Arial
skinparam activity {
  BackgroundColor #E8F4FC
  BorderColor #2E6DA4
}

|#E8F8E8|Problem & scope|
start
:Define goal:\nchild-friendly story generation\nfrom short prompts;
:Constraints:\nGPU memory, latency,\nTinyStories domain;

|#FFF8E8|Data engineering|
:Acquire corpus:\nHugging Face **roneneldan/TinyStories**;
:Tokenize with **GPT-2 BPE**\n(tiktoken), append **<|endoftext|>**\nper story boundary;
:Emit **train.bin** / **val.bin**\n(uint16 memmaps);

|#F0E8FF|Model design|
:Decoder-only **GPT-style**\ntransformer (**SLM**);
:Choices:\nRMSNorm, SwiGLU MLP,\nMHA + SDPA, weight tying,\nlearned positional embeddings;

|#FFE8E8|Training & validation|
:Optimize (**AdamW**, cosine+warmup,\ngrad accumulation, AMP);
:Track **train/val loss**,\nsave **best.pt** / **latest.pt**;

|#E8FFFF|Deployment & evaluation|
:Inference:\n**generate.py** CLI or **server.py**\n(Gradio UI);
:Sample quality review,\nhyperparameter tuning;

stop

@enduml
